<a class="btn btn-default" href="/build/">Build a new course!</a>
<p>These are courses you have saved in the past. You can view, edit (or delete), run, or share these courses.</p>

<h1>Shared Courses</h1>
<p>These are other peoples courses that you have connected to. You can view,update, or connect to these. They automatically update occasionally. Courses are shared via a regattahub.com. They can be openly shared in the database or privately shared via direct link. Privately shared courses can be password protected as well.</p>
  
